videos.headline: BYU RB finds the end zone for early lead
videos.description: BYU running back Lopini Katoa breaks through the hole and scores the 12-yard rushing touchdown.

videos.headline: BYU RB extends the Cougars' lead to 21-0
videos.description: BYU running back Matt Hadley takes the ball and explodes up the field for the 21-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: BYU is rolling in the first half
videos.description: BYU quarterback Zach Collins rolls right and finds Dallin Holker for the 13-yard touchdown.

videos.headline: BYU tacks on with rushing TD
videos.description: Riley Burt runs through tackles and scores the 3-yard rushing touchdown.

videos.headline: Hawaii QB shovels the pass for the TD
videos.description: Hawaii quarterback Dayton Furuta shovels the pass forward to Cole McDonald who finds his way to the end zone for the touchdown.
